## Task

Generate TWO types of tags:

### 1. YouTube Tags (for tag field)

- 2-5 words per tag (long phrases perform better)
- Stay under 500 characters total
- 10-15 tags optimal
- Include: primary keywords, variations, related concepts, long-tail phrases
- Avoid: single generic words, misleading tags

### 2. Description Hashtags (for selection)

Generate 10 hashtags in recommended order. User will select 5.

**Why order matters:**

- First 3 hashtags appear "above the fold" in YouTube description
- These are prime real estate for discoverability
- Order = priority

**Mix of:**

- Niche tags (#bmadmethod, #claudeagentsdk)
- Broader discovery tags (#aicoding, #vibecoding)
- Trending/timely tags if relevant

